sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Admin/Integration
    participant FE as Admin UI or External Sender
    participant API as Backend API (FastAPI)
    participant Q as Queue/Worker (Redis)
    participant PARSER as Document Parser
    participant AI as LLM Service
    participant EMB as Embedding Service
    participant VDB as Vector DB (Chroma)
    participant RDB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>FE: Upload manual or send manufacturer alert
    FE->>API: POST /ingestion endpoint (payload + idempotency-key)
    API->>API: Validate auth/signature and idempotency

    alt Duplicate request
        API-->>FE: 200 Already processed
    else New request
        API->>Q: Enqueue ingestion job
        API-->>FE: 202 Accepted + job_id

        Q->>PARSER: Extract text and split into chunks
        PARSER-->>Q: Chunks + metadata (section/page/machine_type)

        opt Manufacturer alert normalization
            Q->>AI: Normalize and structure alert text
            AI-->>Q: Structured alert fields
        end

        loop For each chunk
            Q->>EMB: Generate embedding
            EMB-->>Q: Embedding vector
            Q->>VDB: Upsert vector + metadata (source, machine_type, section)
        end

        Q->>RDB: Persist ingestion status, references, and errors if any
        Q-->>API: Job complete/fail
        API-->>FE: Status available via polling or webhook callback
    end
